hopobject.body: I can't get through at the moment why would you take clomid if you already ovulate The earth re-absorbed more than 99% of total CO2 emissions last year. Anyone who can do basic arithmetic can refute his claim that CO2 accumulates in the atmosphere. The increase of CO2 in the atmosphere during 2012 was only 4% of human emissions (except for respiration), and therefore only about 1% of total emissions. What a clown to be led into saying such things!
